struct_base.wstring: Modify the options for match settings; score to win, time limit, rounds, spawning, etc...
Modify the options for match settings; score to win, time limit, rounds, spawning, etc...
Sets the number of points required to win a round.
Sets the duration for each round to end on if not enough points have been scored.
Sets the number of regulation rounds in the game (does not include Overtime). Set to 1 for standard, non-round based modes.
Sets the number of won rounds a team needs to end the game.
Sets the number of tied rounds it takes to end the game in a draw.
Modify the options for match settings; score to win, time limit, rounds, spawning, etc...
Sets the duration for the sudden death extension when an objective is actively still in play that could change the match results.
Sets how a tie-score should be handled at the end of Regulation Time.
Sets the duration for the overtime extension duration when the match has resulted in a tie.
Modify the options for match settings; score to win, time limit, rounds, spawning, etc...
Sets how long it takes to respawn.
Sets whether to line-of-sight visibility is taken into account when evaluating respawn point selection.
Sets how much time is added to players respawn timer for self-destructing.
Sets how much time is added to players respawn timer for betraying a teammate.
Modify the options for match settings; score to win, time limit, rounds, spawning, etc...
[ADVANCED] Sets whether machinima controls are enabled for players.
Enable or disable the intro cinematic.
Modify the options sandbox settings; loadouts, weapons, grenades, etc...
Modify the options sandbox settings; loadouts, weapons, grenades, etc...
Sets number of rounds players Primary Weapon spawn with. Non-ammo weapons and values above a weapons maximum capacity are ignored.
Sets number of rounds players Secondary Weapon spawn with. Non-ammo weapons and values above a weapons maximum capacity are ignored.
Sets the number of Frag Grenades players spawn with.
Sets the number of Plasma Grenades players spawn with.
Sets the number of Dynamo Grenades players spawn with.
Sets the number of Spike Grenades players spawn with.
Modify the options sandbox settings; loadouts, weapons, grenades, etc...
Sets whether weapon racks and loose weapons are active in the environment.
Sets whether power weapon pads are active in the environment.
Sets whether weapons can be picked up by players.
Sets whether weapons can be dropped by players (automatically on death and/or manually).
Scales how much damage players deal with weapons.
Sets whether players have infinite ammo with weapons.
Sets whether players have to reload weapons.
Scales how long it takes players to reload when the magazine is not empty.
Scales how long it takes players to reload when the magazine is empty.
Modify the options sandbox settings; loadouts, weapons, grenades, etc...
Sets the maximum number of Frag Grenades players can carry.
Sets the maximum number of Plasma Grenades players can carry.
Sets the maximum number of Dynamo Grenades players can carry.
Sets the maximum number of Spike Grenades players can carry.
Sets whether grenade dispensers and loose grenades are active in the environment.
Sets whether grenades can be picked up by players.
Scales how much damage players deal with grenades.
Scales how long it takes players to throw a grenade.
Scales the area of effect of a grenade explosion.
Scales the distance players are impulsed from grenade explosions.
Modify the options sandbox settings; loadouts, weapons, grenades, etc...
Scales how much damage players deal with melee.
Scales the impulse distance applied to players hit by a melee.
Modify the options sandbox settings; loadouts, weapons, grenades, etc...
Sets whether base equipment dispensers and loose equipment are active in the environment.
Sets whether power equipment pads are active in the environment.
Sets whether equipment can be picked up by players.
Scales the intensity of the Active Camo effect on players.
Sets if players carrying objective items (Flag, ball, etc...) can use equipment.
Modify the options sandbox settings; loadouts, weapons, grenades, etc...
Sets whether vehicle pads and loose vehicles are active in the environment.
Sets whether players can operate vehicle mounted turrets.
Modify the options sandbox settings; loadouts, weapons, grenades, etc...
Sets how long it takes for an unequipped, used weapon to disappear from the map.
Sets how long it takes for an unoccupied, used vehicle to disappear from the map.
Modify the options for HUD settings; Shield/Health Bar & Motion Tracker.
Modify the options for HUD settings; Shield/Health Bar & Motion Tracker.
Sets whether the shield and health bars HUD is visible, or only the health bar is visible.
Sets whether shield HUD effects are enabled; low shield beep, shield flash on damage, and flash effects when shields are down.
Sets whether directional damage HUD indicators are visible.
Modify the options for HUD settings; Shield/Health Bar & Motion Tracker.
Set whether the Motion Tracker is visible.
Sets whether players Motion Tracker is visible when zooming with Smart-link.
Scales the size of the inner ring on the Motion Tracker.
Sets whether players are visible on the Motion Tracker when running (moving faster than crouch-walk).
Sets whether players are visible on the Motion Tracker when sprinting.
Sets whether players are visible on the Motion Tracker when clambering.
Sets whether players are visible on the Motion Tracker when shooting.
Sets whether players are visible on the Motion Tracker when melee lunging.
Modify the options for health & damage tuning.
Modify the options for health & damage tuning.
Sets the ratio of how much damage is resisted by players.
Sets whether headshot bonus damage protection is enabled; on removes extra headshot damage.
Modify the options for health & damage tuning.
Sets whether players can deal damage to their teammates.
Sets the ratio of the damage dealt through Team Damage.
Modify the options for health & damage tuning.
Scales how long it takes for players shields to recharge.
Scales how long it takes for players shields to begin recharging after taking damage.
Sets how much of players' damage to shields is transferred to their own.
Modify the options for health & damage tuning.
Scales how long it takes for players health to recharge.
Scales how long it takes for players health to begin recharging after taking damage.
Sets how much of players' damage to health is transferred to their own.
Modify the options for player movement.
Modify the options for player movement.
Scales players forward/backward movement max speeds.
Scales players forward/backward movement acceleration rate.
Scales players strafing (side-to-side) movement max speeds.
Scales players strafing (side-to-side) movement acceleration rate.
Modify the options for player movement.
Scales how long it takes players to reach Sprint Speed.
Scales how the speed at which players slides.
Scales the maximum distance players travel while sliding.
Sets players ability to reload while sprinting.
Sets whether players shield recharge timer resets when are sprinting.
Sets whether players are knocked out of sprint when taking damage before reaching Sprint Speed.
Modify the options for player movement.
Scales the height of players jumps.
Modify the options for player movement.
Sets whether players can clamber up edges.
Scales how long it takes players to clamber.
Sets the difficulty for bots in the match. Difficulties range from Recruit (for new players) to Spartan (for expert players).
Modify the customization options for bots.
Sets if customization presets should be enabled for bots.
Sets if bot backfill is enabled.
Sets the number of bots on Team 1 (Eagle). The total number of bots on all teams cannot exceed 8.
Sets the number of bots on Team 2 (Cobra). The total number of bots on all teams cannot exceed 8.
Sets the number of bots on Team 3 (Valkyrie). The total number of bots on all teams cannot exceed 8.
Sets the number of bots on Team 4 (Rampart). The total number of bots on all teams cannot exceed 8.
Sets the number of bots on Team 5 (Cutlass). The total number of bots on all teams cannot exceed 8.
Sets the number of bots on Team 6 (Cutlass). The total number of bots on all teams cannot exceed 8.
Sets the number of bots on Team 7 (Valor). The total number of bots on all teams cannot exceed 8.
Sets the number of bots on Team 8 (Hazard). The total number of bots on all teams cannot exceed 8.
Sets the number of participants in a Free-For-All game. If there are less than 8 players, bots will fill in the remaining openings.
Modify the game mode options for Slayer.
Sets the number of points players earns for slaying an enemy.
Sets the number of points players lose for self-destructing.
Sets the number of points lost for betraying a teammate.
Sets the number of points players earn for assisting in the slaying of an enemy.
Sets the number of points scored (or lost) on death.
Sets the number of additional points players earn for slaying an enemy with a headshot.
Sets the number of additional points players earn for slaying an enemy with a beatdown.
Sets the number of additional points players earn for slaying an enemy with a vehicle splatter.
Sets the number of additional points players earn for slaying an enemy with a plasma grenade stick.
Modify game options for Capture the Flag.
Sets how many points are awarded per Flag capture.
Sets whether teams need to have their Flag at home in order to score.
Sets how many Flags each team has active at a time.
Set how the flag carrier's marker appears.
Sets how long a revealed Flag carrier player has a nav-marker on them.
Sets whether the Flag carrier is spotted when taking damage.
Sets whether the Flag carrier is spotted when sprinting.
Sets how long it takes for the Flag to return to stand after it has been dropped.
Sets whether Flags return to stand instantly when touched.
Scales the Flag carrier's maximum shield value.
Scales the Flag carrier's maximum health value.
Scales the Flag carrier's movement speed.
Sets whether the Flag carrier can sprint.
Scales the Flag carrier's gravitational acceleration.
Modify the game mode options for Attrition.
Sets the number of shared Team Respawns. Respawning will be disabled for a team once these respawns are depleted.
Sets whether slaying enemies rewards additional Respawns to a team.
Sets whether players can be revived when eliminated; causing them to drop their AI Revive Orb for allies to interact with to revive them.
Sets how long ally players must interact with the Revive Orb to revive the player.
Sets whether the shrinking Danger Zone becomes active when both Teams Respawn Count reaches 0.
Sets the incoming time the Danger Zone will wait before it begins to shrink
Sets whether the Capture Zone is used in the mode. Capturing it will win the round for the capturing team.
Sets how long before the Capture Zone becomes active.
Sets how long the Capture Zone is incoming once it becomes active.
Sets how long players must be inside the capture zone to capture it.
Modify the game mode options for King of the Hill.
Whether to grant points immediately or only when a bank is full
How much score to grant at a time
How many seconds to wait before moving to the next hill
Health multiplier for players inside the hill
Shield multiplier for players inside the hill
Shield recharge rate multiplier for players inside the hill
Weapon damage multiplier for players inside the hill
Melee damage multiplier for players inside the hill
Player movement speed while inside the hill
Player sprint top speed while inside the hill
Player slide speed while inside the hill
How long players will slide inside the hill
Whether players can sprint while inside the hill
Modify the game mode options for Oddball.
Set how many points are earned for carrying the ball.
Set how often points are awarded for carrying the ball.
Set how long the initial delay is before skulls spawn.
Sets whether the Flag carrier can sprint.
Sets the number of points scored at each time interval.
Sets how often points are scored.
Sets the minimum number of Strongholds a team must control to score points.
Sets how long players must be inside a Stronghold zone to capture it.

Sets what happens when there are multiple members of a team in the Stronghold. Decreasing/increasing rates will make each additional player contribute less/more towards heightening the overall capture rate.
Sets whether teams start the game with captured Strongholds. Initial ownership is determined based on distance to team initial spawns.
Sets whether contesting a Stronghold prevents it from score scoring.
Sets how many enemies it takes to contest a Stronghold.
Sets whether players are prevented from spawning within the boundary of a Stronghold.
Sets the point difference needed to end the game during Sudden Death.
Sets the additional time penalty added to respawn duration while in Sudden Death.
Sets if the player has Infinite Ammo.
Sets the amount of Friendly bots.
Determines the amount of bots in the Enemy Team.
Sets bot skill in a practice match.
Sets if bots should playfight instead of shoot.
Sets if you can see bots through walls in a practice match.
Number of infected players on round start
Starting infected players gain additional traits when enabled
If enabled, Last Spartan Standing traits will be given to the last remaining survivors
If enabled, Last Spartan Standing traits will be given to all survivors in the final seconds of the round
Last Spartan Standing players receive a navpoint when enabled
Do survivors become infected on suicide
Infected players gain a surrounding aura of pestilence when enabled
Swords wielded by infected players gain a gruesome glow when enabled

Which type of ball will be used by the mode.
Enable or disable damage for the ball delivery explosion.

How long it takes to deliver the ball when it's not being carried.

How long it takes for delivery progress to reset as a delivering team member.

How long it takes for delivery progress to reset as a non-delivering team member.
Points scored for delivering when carrying the ball.
Points scored for delivering by throwing the ball.
Points scored for carrying the ball.
How often points are scored for carrying the ball.
The number of points earned for killing an enemy with the ball while carrying.
The number of points earned for killing an enemy.
The number of points lost for committing suicide.
The number of points lost for betraying a teammate.
How long it takes for the ball to respawn.
How long it takes for the first ball to spawn.
Time added to the ball's next respawn after a team delivers the ball.
